<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><entry xmlns:my="http://example.com/my" xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="entry_ærxūd" xml:lang="os"><form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>ærxūd</orth></form><form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>ærxodæ</orth><form type="variant"><orth>ærmxodæ</orth></form></form><sense><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>рукавица</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>mitten</q></cit></sense><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>перчатка</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>glove</q></cit></sense></sense><cit type="exampleGroup" corresp="#sense_ærxūd." n=""><cit type="example"><quote>ænæ ærxūdæj kʼūxtæ syjync</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>без рукавиц руки мерзнут</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>hands freeze without mittens</q></cit></cit></cit><cit type="exampleGroup" corresp="#sense_." n=""><cit type="example"><quote>ænæ ærxūdæj kʼūxtæ syjync</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>без рукавиц руки мерзнут</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>hands freeze without mittens</q></cit></cit></cit><etym xml:lang="ru">Сложение %iarm-xūd%i(← *%iarma-xauda%i), буквально „шапка руки“. Для выпадения %im%i ср. <xr><ref target="#entry_ardwan"/><ref target="#entry_ærʒæf"/></xr>. Другое слово для ‘рукавицы’— <xr><ref target="#entry_ærmkʼūx"/></xr> q. v. См. также <xr><ref target="#entry_arm"/></xr> ‘рука’ и <xr><ref target="#entry_xūd"/></xr> ‘шапка’.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">It is a complex word %iarm-xūd%i (← *%iarma-xauda%i), literally 'hand's cap'. which literally means „hand’s cap “. For the loss of m compare <xr><ref target="#entry_ardwan"/><ref target="#entry_ærʒæf"/></xr>. Another word for ‘mitten’ is <xr><ref target="#entry_ærmkʼūx"/></xr> q. v. See also <xr><ref target="#entry_arm"/></xr> ‘hand’ and <xr><ref target="#entry_xūd"/></xr> ‘cap’.</etym></entry>